(365, 'Notes:: **Founders** [**Sandeep Aggarwal**](https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandeep-aggarwal-1a827415/)[** **](https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandeep-aggarwal-1a827415/)- Head Banking and Partnership Alliances @ PayU (~4 yrs), Head Sales and Portfolio - Merchant Acq Biz @ IndusInd (2.5 yrs) , Head ECom and Key Accounts North and East @ Axis Bank (9.5 yrs), Manager Key Accounts @ HDFC Bank (1 yr) [**Arvind Singh**](https://www.linkedin.com/in/arvind-singh-a324341a/) - Business Head Commercial and Business Cards @ IndusInd (~9 yrs 8 mos), TMCs and Alliances @ Axis Bank (6 yrs),  Business Manager Corporate Cards @ ICICI (2 yrs) **Overview- ** Solving B2B payment workflows and  working capital lines using commercial cards. Planning to start by focusing on the travel segment as a vertical, allow smaller OTAs and travel agents to access credit while booking flights (will tie up with IATA over here). **Views** **TT- Weak Maybe** **Overall- **Interesting thesis vis-a-vis B2B payments and vertical focused workflow solving (travel), However founder archetype (Sales profile + muddled thought process ) + lack of courage of conviction( neither of the founders have quit yet) breaks it for me in the first meeting. Will need consistent rockstar refs to consider for MPI Seed. + Interesting thesis- B2B payments + verticalized value using commercial cards --- starting with travel + Founders have spent 10 K hours in the space (albeit in sales roles) ?Muddled thought process- not completely clear on the...')
